00:43.480 --> 00:48.646
<font color="#808080">KELLER:</font> <i>Our Father, who art in heaven,
hallowed be thy name.</i>

00:49.280 --> 00:51.123
<i>Thy kingdom come...</i>

00:51.600 --> 00:55.241
<i>...thy will be done,
on earth as it is in heaven.</i>

00:56.240 --> 00:59.289
<i>Give us this day our daily bread...</i>

00:59.800 --> 01:02.485
<i>...and forgive us our trespasses...</i>

01:02.920 --> 01:06.481
<i>...as we forgive those
who trespass against us.</i>

01:08.280 --> 01:10.851
<i>Lead us not into temptation...</i>

01:11.560 --> 01:13.642
<i>...but deliver us from evil.</i>

01:15.200 --> 01:19.842
<i>For the kingdom, the power
and the glory are yours...</i>

01:20.440 --> 01:22.363
<i>...now and forever.</i>

01:23.520 --> 01:25.045
<i>Amen.</i>

01:29.720 --> 01:31.768
<font color="#D900D9">(BIRD SQUAWKING)</font>

01:39.960 --> 01:42.247
<font color="#D900D9">(THUNDER RUMBLES)</font>

01:42.960 --> 01:46.806
<font color="#808080">WEATHERMAN:</font> <i>Looking at mostly cloudy skies
and with lows in the upper 20s...</i>

01:47.000 --> 01:49.526
<i>...there will be some refreeze
on some of the roads...</i>

01:49.680 --> 01:52.490
<i>...so slick spots are possible tonight
in isolated...</i>

01:54.600 --> 01:57.843
You know the most important thing
your granddad ever taught me?

01:58.720 --> 02:00.131
Hmm?

02:02.840 --> 02:04.330
Be ready.

02:06.720 --> 02:11.442
Hurricane, flood,
whatever it ends up being.

02:11.720 --> 02:16.044
No more food gets delivered
to the grocery store, gas stations dry up.

02:16.360 --> 02:18.886
People just turn on each other, and, uh...

02:20.360 --> 02:24.081
All of a sudden, all that stands
between you and being dead is you.

02:29.960 --> 02:31.564
I'm proud of you, son.

02:32.920 --> 02:34.490
It was a nice shot.

02:41.040 --> 02:46.080
<font color="#D900D9">(GENE MacLELLAN'S "PUT YOUR HAND
IN THE HAND" PLAYING OVER THE RADIO)</font>

02:46.240 --> 02:52.885
<i>Put your hand in the hand of the man
Who stilled the water</i>

02:53.200 --> 02:59.810
<i>Put your hand in the hand of the man
Who calmed the sea</i>

03:00.120 --> 03:03.602
<i>Take a look at yourself
And you can look at others differently</i>

03:03.760 --> 03:07.082
<font color="#D900D9">(DOG BARKING)</font>

03:14.680 --> 03:20.847
<i>Every time I look into the holy book
I wanna tremble</i>

03:30.760 --> 03:31.921
<font color="#808080">GRACE:</font> Hey, come on, hon.

03:32.080 --> 03:34.003
<font color="#D900D9">(ANNA HUMMING)</font>

03:34.160 --> 03:36.970
<font color="#808080">GRACE:</font> Wait. I forgot something.
Hold on a second, Anna!

03:37.120 --> 03:39.009
<font color="#808080">KELLER:</font> Ralph, you have the venison?
<font color="#808080">RALPH:</font> Yup.

03:39.200 --> 03:40.804
<font color="#808080">GRACE:</font> I forgot the pie.

03:40.960 --> 03:44.043
<font color="#D900D9">(ANNA CONTINUES HUMMING)</font>

03:44.240 --> 03:45.321
Are we taking the truck?

03:45.480 --> 03:47.801
We're going up the street, you dope.

03:50.880 --> 03:52.405
Come on.

03:54.160 --> 03:56.447
<font color="#808080">GRACE:</font> Hey, wait for your mother, please.

03:56.600 --> 03:58.648
Give me a ride.

04:00.840 --> 04:03.002
<font color="#808080">KELLER:</font> Oh, you're getting heavy.

04:03.680 --> 04:06.365
<font color="#808080">RALPH:</font> Danny's dad said
he'd sell me their old car.

04:06.520 --> 04:08.761
I got half of what I need saved
from the summer.

04:08.920 --> 04:10.410
- I thought maybe...
- Forget it.

04:10.600 --> 04:13.763
I can barely get enough carpentry work
to keep up with the mortgage.

04:14.600 --> 04:17.285
Why don't you rent out Grandpa's
old apartment house?

04:17.480 --> 04:18.685
<font color="#D900D9">(GRACE CHUCKLES)</font>

04:18.839 --> 04:23.084
Like I keep telling your mother, it's an old building.
It'll cost a fortune to fix it up.

04:28.640 --> 04:30.529
<font color="#808080">KELLER:</font> Oh.

04:33.840 --> 04:35.569
<font color="#D900D9">(RALPH COUGHS)</font>

04:36.440 --> 04:37.965
<font color="#D900D9">(DOORBELL RINGING)</font>

04:38.120 --> 04:39.849
<font color="#808080">KELLER:</font> Hey.
<font color="#808080">GRACE:</font> Okay, okay.

04:40.000 --> 04:41.604
<font color="#808080">NANCY:</font> They're here!

04:41.800 --> 04:44.371
<font color="#D900D9">(CLASSICAL MUSIC PLAYING
FROM SPEAKER)</font>

04:44.520 --> 04:47.205
<font color="#808080">GRACE:</font> - Hello.
- Happy Thanksgiving.

04:47.360 --> 04:48.921
<font color="#808080">KELLER:</font> Anna, wait until we're invited.

04:49.040 --> 04:50.883
For God's sake, Keller.
Get the hell in here.

04:51.040 --> 04:52.440
<font color="#D900D9">(FRANKLIN YELLS THEN GIRLS SCREAMS)</font>

04:52.560 --> 04:54.164
<font color="#D900D9">(FRANKLIN LAUGHS)</font>

04:54.320 --> 04:56.239
<font color="#808080">RALPH:</font> - Happy Thanksgiving.
- Happy Turkey Day.

04:56.240 --> 04:58.971
- Keller, got the deer you shot?
- This one's Ralph's.

04:59.120 --> 05:01.771
- You killed it, you take it into the kitchen.
- Thank you.

05:01.920 --> 05:04.526
<font color="#808080">FRANKLIN:</font> I loved that last meal you gave us.
<font color="#808080">KELLER:</font> There he is.

05:04.680 --> 05:06.409
- Thank you. Happy T-Day.
<font color="#808080">KELLER:</font> - How are you?

05:06.560 --> 05:08.608
<font color="#808080">NANCY:</font> All right.
<font color="#808080">KELLER:</font> Good to see you.

05:08.760 --> 05:12.845
<font color="#808080">NANCY:</font> Joy, three times.
Joy, get those dolls off the table.

05:13.040 --> 05:15.202
<font color="#808080">KELLER:</font> Anna! Anna!
<font color="#808080">ELIZA:</font> Hi. How are you?

05:15.360 --> 05:16.646
<font color="#808080">KELLER:</font> Happy Thanksgiving.

05:16.800 --> 05:18.723
- Hi, Eliza.
- Anna, come here.

05:19.360 --> 05:21.727
We wait until we're invited,
you understand?

05:21.920 --> 05:24.082
<font color="#808080">NANCY:</font> You're in charge of this.

05:24.240 --> 05:26.971
Us veterinarians make lousy butchers.

05:27.120 --> 05:28.770
No problem.

05:31.440 --> 05:32.851
<font color="#808080">ANNA:</font> Can I go outside with Joy?

05:33.000 --> 05:36.209
Uh, convince your brother
to go with you and you can.

05:38.560 --> 05:41.245
And wear a hat, please.
You're just getting over a cold.

05:41.440 --> 05:43.408
Joy, you wear a hat too.

05:45.560 --> 05:48.086
<font color="#808080">ELIZA:</font> <i>Did you feel bad for
that deer when you shot it?</i>

05:48.920 --> 05:52.003
<font color="#808080">RALPH:</font> Do you feel bad for cows
when you go to McDonald's?

05:52.760 --> 05:55.889
That's what my dad says.
Deer, if they have too many babies...

05:56.080 --> 05:59.163
...the babies starve anyway.
You gotta keep the population down.

05:59.320 --> 06:00.765
Right.

06:01.280 --> 06:03.567
- Your dad say that too?
<font color="#808080">JOY:</font> - Pull harder.

06:04.640 --> 06:06.563
Hey! Get away from that thing!

06:06.760 --> 06:08.205
Let me see that.

06:08.360 --> 06:10.442
- Come on, let's go.
- No.

06:10.640 --> 06:11.721
<font color="#808080">RALPH:</font> I said, let's go!

06:11.880 --> 06:14.565
<font color="#808080">ELIZA:</font> Stop. Stop. You can't just hit
somebody's stuff like that.

06:14.720 --> 06:18.167
- No! Let's go! Come on, come on.
- Let me...!

06:18.480 --> 06:21.131
Wait. You hear that?

06:21.920 --> 06:23.968
Somebody's in there.

06:24.240 --> 06:27.767
I don't feel like getting yelled at.
Let's go. Don't climb up, okay?

06:27.920 --> 06:29.809
<font color="#D900D9">("PUT YOUR HAND IN THE HAND"
CONTINUES PLAYING OVER THE RADIO)</font>

06:29.960 --> 06:33.043
<font color="#D900D9">(RALPH & ANNA
INDISTINCTLY CHATTERING)</font>

06:33.240 --> 06:37.245
<i>And it causes me shame to know
We're not the people we should be</i>

06:39.240 --> 06:42.562
<font color="#808080">FRANKLIN:</font> The school board's telling me
there's no money for new band uniforms.

06:42.720 --> 06:45.644
Kids are wearing the same uniforms
they had when we went there.

06:45.840 --> 06:48.650
They were old then.
I mean, marching right out of 1979.

06:49.760 --> 06:51.888
Why isn't he speaking to me?

06:52.040 --> 06:53.883
He doesn't speak.

06:55.000 --> 06:56.843
- Cutie pie.
- Mm-hm.

06:57.000 --> 06:58.650
- Oh, my gosh!
- Whoa.

06:58.800 --> 07:00.962
- He's fast too.
- Mm.

07:01.120 --> 07:03.646
He's so quick. Is that a slide?

07:03.800 --> 07:06.610
<font color="#808080">FRANKLIN:</font> Thank y'all. Thank y'all.
Got a surprise.

07:06.760 --> 07:08.603
<font color="#808080">NANCY:</font> Oh.

07:08.800 --> 07:12.009
And I am taking requests.

07:12.200 --> 07:13.770
- Yes! Yes.
- No.

07:13.920 --> 07:16.207
<font color="#D900D9">(ALL LAUGHING)</font>

07:16.360 --> 07:17.521
Okay.

07:17.680 --> 07:20.126
You gotta listen out for it
because this is not easy.

07:20.280 --> 07:22.442
Mommy, can I take Joy to our house?

07:22.600 --> 07:24.409
- Why?
- My red whistle.

07:24.560 --> 07:26.210
She's gonna help me look for it.

07:26.360 --> 07:29.091
Sweetheart, I think that red whistle
is long gone.

07:29.240 --> 07:30.366
<font color="#808080">NANCY:</font> What whistle?

07:30.520 --> 07:33.808
The emergency whistle Daddy gave me.
I lost it...

07:36.000 --> 07:38.571
...a hundred and 33 days ago.

07:39.160 --> 07:43.370
Well, if you want to find a whistle,
you have to whistle for it.

07:43.560 --> 07:45.688
So we'll do "Jingle Bells" to find it.

07:45.920 --> 07:49.322
<font color="#D900D9">(FRANKLIN WHISTLING "JINGLE BELLS")</font>

07:50.360 --> 07:53.807
<font color="#808080">BOTH:</font> <font color="#D900D9">(SINGING)</font> <i>Jingle Bells, Batman smells
Robin laid an egg</i>

07:53.960 --> 07:56.566
<i>The Batmobile lost its wheel
And Joker got away</i>

07:56.720 --> 07:58.165
<font color="#808080">KELLER:</font> Okay.
<font color="#808080">GRACE:</font> Yay!

07:58.720 --> 08:01.246
Okay! Okay. You can go. All right.

08:01.400 --> 08:04.449
Just make sure Eliza
and Ralph go with you, please.

08:05.560 --> 08:07.324
- No looking in the basement.
- I won't.

08:07.480 --> 08:10.563
Your eardrums are starting to grow.
Don't want to damage them yet.

08:10.760 --> 08:13.206
- But I am taking requests from you, Keller.
- From me?

08:13.360 --> 08:16.409
<font color="#808080">FRANKLIN:</font> - Your day, your request.
- Oh. Uh, the piano.

08:16.560 --> 08:19.245
<font color="#808080">FRANKLIN:</font> - No. So all set?
- No, no, no.

08:19.400 --> 08:22.529
Wait, listen. He used to love...
He used to dress like Springsteen.

08:22.680 --> 08:24.921
<font color="#808080">KELLER:</font> I still love Springsteen.
<font color="#808080">GRACE:</font> "Jersey Girl."

08:25.080 --> 08:30.883
Well, I ain't white, and I like him too
much, and I'm too drunk to cover The Boss.

08:31.040 --> 08:32.451
- Thank you.
<font color="#808080">FRANKLIN:</font> - Honey?

08:32.600 --> 08:35.001
<font color="#808080">GRACE:</font> - What else?
- Nothing comes to mind. Nothing.

08:35.200 --> 08:37.009
<font color="#808080">GRACE:</font> Oh, I know.
<font color="#808080">KELLER:</font> What?

08:37.200 --> 08:41.284
He actually loves "The Star-Spangled Banner." I know.
Sings it in the shower.

08:41.440 --> 08:43.442
- I do not.
- Yes, you do!

08:43.600 --> 08:44.761
<font color="#808080">FRANKLIN:</font> I got you.

08:46.120 --> 08:50.603
<font color="#D900D9">(PLAYING "THE STAR-SPANGLED
BANNER")</font>

09:08.640 --> 09:15.649
<font color="#D900D9">(CHATTERING ON TV)</font>

09:18.480 --> 09:20.164
Where are your sisters?

09:20.560 --> 09:22.324
I can't find them.

09:22.720 --> 09:25.200
You, uh, go to the house with them?

09:25.360 --> 09:27.169
No. What are you talking about?

09:27.320 --> 09:29.641
- Earlier?
- No.

09:29.800 --> 09:33.521
What? They were supposed to come down
earlier and get you. They didn't come?

09:33.680 --> 09:35.489
No. We haven't seen them since we ate.

09:35.640 --> 09:38.325
It's all right. They're
probably at our house.

09:43.160 --> 09:47.051
<font color="#D900D9">(DOG BARKING)</font>

09:51.920 --> 09:53.365
<font color="#808080">KELLER:</font> Anna?

09:53.520 --> 09:55.329
Joy?

09:57.160 --> 09:58.685
Anna?

09:59.960 --> 10:01.450
Girls?

10:20.960 --> 10:22.166
Girls?

10:23.040 --> 10:24.883
- Who put these in here?
- Get out of here.

10:25.040 --> 10:28.647
- They weren't outside. It's starting to rain.
- Did you check by Maria's swing?

10:28.800 --> 10:30.211
Yeah.

10:30.560 --> 10:34.007
They're getting whupped when
they get here. Sorry, Grace. I whup kids.

10:34.160 --> 10:35.844
What? So they weren't there either?

10:36.000 --> 10:37.889
- They must be at home.
<font color="#808080">KELLER:</font> - Are they here?

10:38.240 --> 10:40.720
- They weren't there?
- No, they're not at the house.

10:40.880 --> 10:41.927
They're not there.

10:42.160 --> 10:44.686
<font color="#808080">ELIZA:</font> I checked the entire house.
They're not here.

10:46.440 --> 10:48.442
The RV.

10:48.600 --> 10:51.251
Dad, there was this RV
and they were playing on it.

10:51.400 --> 10:53.801
There was...
We thought there was someone inside.

10:54.000 --> 10:55.206
<font color="#808080">FRANKLIN:</font> - Wait, nobody...
- Where?

10:55.360 --> 10:57.089
Where was it? Show me.

10:57.240 --> 10:59.163
- You wait here.
<font color="#808080">NANCY:</font> - Let me go!

10:59.320 --> 11:01.720
- I'm gonna search the house again.
<font color="#808080">FRANKLIN:</font> - Relax. Relax.

11:03.840 --> 11:06.366
<font color="#808080">KELLER:</font> Go that way. I'll
meet you on the other side.

11:07.360 --> 11:08.771
Anna?

11:08.920 --> 11:10.490
<font color="#808080">FRANKLIN:</font> Joy!

11:11.600 --> 11:13.648
<font color="#D900D9">(THUNDER RUMBLING)</font>

11:14.120 --> 11:18.170
- Roger, you seen my daughter walk by here?
- No. ls there a problem?

11:21.440 --> 11:22.965
<font color="#808080">KELLER:</font> Anna?

11:23.280 --> 11:26.443
<font color="#808080">RALPH:</font> Here! Dad, it was parked right here.

11:28.600 --> 11:31.649
<font color="#808080">KELLER:</font> Anna? Anna?

11:33.680 --> 11:35.284
- Hello, hello!
<font color="#808080">FRANKLIN:</font> - Did you see them?

11:35.440 --> 11:37.602
<font color="#808080">RALPH:</font> - No!
- Hello!

11:38.400 --> 11:41.847
- I couldn't find them!
- Were you messing around in this house?

11:42.000 --> 11:43.601
<font color="#808080">RALPH:</font> - No.
- Told you not to come here.

11:43.720 --> 11:45.802
They were on the RV
and we got them off of it.

11:45.960 --> 11:48.281
Tell me everything you remember
about that RV.

11:48.440 --> 11:51.808
- A ladder on the back.
- Police, police.

12:03.960 --> 12:05.883
Happy Thanksgiving.

12:06.040 --> 12:10.409
<font color="#808080">LOKI:</font> Thanks. Hey, you have any of those
fortune cookie things?

12:10.560 --> 12:13.484
My boss told me cops
don't like fortune cookies.

12:14.480 --> 12:18.326
What year were you born? Are you a
dragon or a snake or a horse, or...?

12:18.480 --> 12:20.005
I'm a monkey.

12:20.480 --> 12:21.811
Oh, you're a monkey.

12:23.520 --> 12:28.686
You're very intelligent.
You have an ability to influence people.

12:28.840 --> 12:32.128
Think you could influence your boss
to lower the check a little bit?

12:32.280 --> 12:37.127
No. I cannot. My boss is a rooster.

12:43.080 --> 12:45.731
So he's selfish and eccentric, that's...

12:49.000 --> 12:51.526
<font color="#D900D9">(CELL PHONE BUZZING)</font>

12:52.200 --> 12:55.727
<font color="#808080">DISPATCHER:</font> <i>All units, all units. An RV
was reported matching the description.</i>

12:55.920 --> 13:00.687
<i>The vehicle is parked at a rest stop
off of Route 46, northbound, past exit 17.</i>

13:00.880 --> 13:02.291
<i>Any available units?</i>

13:02.440 --> 13:04.442
<font color="#808080">POLICEMAN 1:</font> <font color="#D900D9">(OVER RADIO)</font>
<i>This is 12-12 responding.</i>

13:05.040 --> 13:06.724
<font color="#808080">POLICEMAN 2:</font> <font color="#D900D9">(OVER RADIO)</font>
<i>10-80 responding.</i>

13:06.880 --> 13:11.204
This is 13-40. I'm five minutes out.
I'll meet the responding units.

13:30.840 --> 13:34.242
<font color="#808080">POLICEMAN 1:</font> <i>12-12 standing by.</i>
<font color="#808080">POLICEMAN 2:</font> <i>10-80 standing by.</i>

13:34.400 --> 13:38.246
13-40. I am on-scene.
Be advised, we are moving in.

14:14.880 --> 14:17.121
<font color="#D900D9">(ENGINE REVVING)</font>

14:18.760 --> 14:20.046
<font color="#808080">LOKI:</font> Don't move, wait!

14:20.200 --> 14:21.201
Whoa. Whoa!

14:21.360 --> 14:25.285
<font color="#808080">POLICEMAN 1:</font> Watch out!
<font color="#808080">LOKI:</font> Hey! Don't shoot! Don't shoot!

14:27.360 --> 14:28.521
Don't shoot!

14:28.880 --> 14:29.961
Don't shoot!

14:37.720 --> 14:39.609
<font color="#808080">LOKI:</font> All right, Sloan, take the right!

14:47.640 --> 14:49.165
<font color="#808080">POLICEMAN 1:</font> Clear!

14:55.080 --> 14:56.491
<font color="#808080">POLICEMAN 2:</font> Clear!

14:59.360 --> 15:02.170
Hey! Wait, wait, wait. I got this.

15:02.320 --> 15:04.049
Give me that.

15:25.160 --> 15:26.491
Hey.

15:26.640 --> 15:30.042
Hey, I see you in there.
Show me both your hands right now.

15:30.240 --> 15:32.846
Hey! I see you in there.
Show me your hands!

15:35.440 --> 15:37.681
Both hands right now!

15:38.200 --> 15:43.525
Nice and slow. Slow. Slow! Slow.
Slowly. Both hands.

15:44.000 --> 15:46.048
Both fucking hands!

15:46.760 --> 15:48.205
<font color="#D900D9">(GRUNTING)</font>

15:48.360 --> 15:50.840
<font color="#808080">LOKI:</font> Walk! Walk!

15:54.040 --> 15:56.805
Walk! Get up! Get up!

15:58.720 --> 16:00.165
Get up!

16:00.520 --> 16:03.603
Show me those girls!
Show me where you put those girls.

16:04.520 --> 16:08.411
Where are those girls?
Where are those girls?

16:08.560 --> 16:10.130
- Give me the flashlight.
<font color="#808080">POLICEMAN 1:</font> - Sir.

16:10.320 --> 16:12.641
Show me where those girls...
They in the woods?

16:12.800 --> 16:14.928
You put them in the woods?

16:16.040 --> 16:18.361
Where did you put those girls?

16:20.240 --> 16:21.890
You hear me?

16:23.400 --> 16:25.084
What the fuck is this guy on?

16:25.920 --> 16:27.410
No, he's high on something.

16:27.560 --> 16:30.006
Put this fucking guy in the car.
Get him in the car.

16:30.160 --> 16:32.811
- Put him in the fucking car! Walk!
- Let's go.

16:33.560 --> 16:36.564
Hey, call P.S.P.,
tell them to send their scent dogs.

16:36.760 --> 16:40.048
And seal off the whole area.
The entrance, all of it.

16:40.200 --> 16:43.124
<font color="#808080">POLICEMAN 1:</font> - Right.
- You, come with me.

16:43.480 --> 16:46.006
<font color="#808080">LOKI:</font> No, they weren't playing on your RV?

16:46.160 --> 16:47.605
No.

16:47.760 --> 16:50.240
<font color="#D900D9">(LOKI GASPS THEN SIGHS)</font>

16:53.720 --> 16:55.563
Okay, take a look at them again.

16:57.600 --> 17:00.888
- Don't recognize these girls?
- I didn't see them. May I sit down?

17:01.080 --> 17:02.320
<font color="#808080">LOKI:</font> <i>What do you do in the RV?</i>

17:02.440 --> 17:03.930
<i>- Answer my questions.</i>
<font color="#808080">ALEX:</font> <i>- Sleep there.</i>

17:04.119 --> 17:07.806
<font color="#808080">LOKI:</font> <i>You sleep in there?
