17:30.040 --> 17:32.327
<font color="#808080">LOKI:</font> <i>Did you ask them to come inside?</i>
<font color="#808080">ALEX:</font> <i>No.</i>

17:32.480 --> 17:33.799
<font color="#808080">LOKI:</font> <i>You ask them to come in...</i>

