17:39.560 --> 17:41.688
I know you put those girls somewhere.

17:42.800 --> 17:44.086
- You hide them?
- No.

17:44.240 --> 17:46.686
How did you hide them.
Did you tie them up?

17:46.840 --> 17:48.444
- Did you tie them up?
- Hmm.

17:48.600 --> 17:50.887
Huh? Hey. Hey.

17:51.280 --> 17:52.691
Hey.

17:54.840 --> 17:57.764
Look, I know you're a good guy.
I know you're a decent guy.

17:57.920 --> 18:00.002
<i>I'm not telling you
you're doing anything bad.</i>

18:00.160 --> 18:03.687
<i>I'm just trying to get the right answers.
