18:03.840 --> 18:06.411
Where do you usually park your RV, Alex?

18:06.680 --> 18:07.727
My aunt's house.

18:07.880 --> 18:08.927
<font color="#808080">LOKI:</font> <i>Your aunt's house?</i>

18:09.080 --> 18:10.889
<font color="#808080">ALEX:</font> <i>She lets me park it in the back yard.</i>

18:11.040 --> 18:14.647
<i>Grass don't grow back there anyway.</i>

18:16.160 --> 18:18.367
<font color="#808080">AUNT:</font> It was my husband's.

18:18.520 --> 18:20.887
For sale, if you want it.

18:25.200 --> 18:26.531
No, thanks.

18:27.360 --> 18:30.682
Would you tell me
what you're doing on my property then?

18:33.040 --> 18:36.203
I'm just glad to know where he is.

18:36.360 --> 18:40.365
He's always home before dark, and...

18:40.520 --> 18:41.885
...I just don't understand.

18:42.040 --> 18:45.567
That boy has never been in trouble,
not a day in his life.

18:47.720 --> 18:52.169
In the summertime,
he sleeps out in the camper some, but...

18:52.320 --> 18:56.325
...this time of year he sleeps
in here on the sofa bed.

19:05.320 --> 19:07.243
That's my husband.

19:07.400 --> 19:11.405
We had a fight, jeez, five years ago.

19:13.600 --> 19:16.126
Walked out, didn't come back.

19:17.440 --> 19:20.364
Alex loved him like a father.

19:23.400 --> 19:25.607
<font color="#808080">LOKI:</font> Where are Alex's real parents?

19:25.760 --> 19:27.888
My husband's brother and his girlfriend...

19:28.040 --> 19:32.170
