when Alex was about 6.

19:32.320 --> 19:34.084
<font color="#808080">LOKI:</font> Sorry to hear that.

19:43.920 --> 19:46.127
He doesn't have much.

19:52.640 --> 19:54.290
What have you got?

19:54.440 --> 19:58.650
Well, this thing's clean. I mean, it's
filthy as shit, but we didn't find anything.

19:58.840 --> 20:01.650
