I might buy that.

20:09.640 --> 20:12.689
But if there had been a struggle,
I would have found something.

20:12.840 --> 20:15.650
I'd start looking in the woods
by the rest stop.

20:16.120 --> 20:19.920
Yeah, half the uniformed cops
in the state are doing that right now.

20:20.520 --> 20:24.206
When you're done with this thing, can you
send a crew over to the aunt's house?

20:27.960 --> 20:32.568
<font color="#D900D9">(INDISTINCT CHATTERING)</font>

20:46.480 --> 20:48.005
Anna?

20:54.120 --> 20:55.884
Anna?

21:25.920 --> 21:28.048
<font color="#808080">FRANKLIN:</font> Thanks for coming.
Franklin Birch.

21:28.200 --> 21:30.282
My wife's in here.

21:31.160 --> 21:34.642
Honey? Her name's Nancy.

21:34.800 --> 21:37.565
Detective Loki is... Honey?

21:44.440 --> 21:47.250
These photos are better
than the ones my husband gave you.

21:47.400 --> 21:49.926
You can see her eyes more clearly.

22:17.600 --> 22:19.090
<font color="#808080">GRACE:</font> So did we pass?

22:20.640 --> 22:22.608
I'm sorry, what did you say?

22:23.320 --> 22:26.483
The poly thing, the lie detector
we took this morning.

22:26.640 --> 22:28.483
Did we pass?

22:29.360 --> 22:30.850
Oh, yeah. Sorry.

22:32.480 --> 22:35.324
Yes. We appreciate your cooperation.

22:37.040 --> 22:40.442
It's embarrassing, all the...
All this fuss.

22:41.720 --> 22:43.449
Everyone's gonna think we're crazy...

22:43.600 --> 22:46.649
...when those two come out of hiding,
wherever they are.

22:47.920 --> 22:50.844
Do you have some reason
to believe they ran away?

22:51.000 --> 22:52.490
No.

22:54.200 --> 22:56.123
They're happy.

22:59.600 --> 23:02.001
They must have run away.

23:02.960 --> 23:06.362
I think they must have run away. Right?

23:08.440 --> 23:09.771
Um...

23:10.960 --> 23:14.965
Your police captain told me
that you've solved every case...

23:15.160 --> 23:18.084
...that you've ever been assigned.
Is that right?

23:25.160 --> 23:26.650
Sorry.

23:28.840 --> 23:33.971
I am so sorry.
Do you have children, detective?

23:40.520 --> 23:42.682
I'm gonna find your daughter.

23:44.800 --> 23:48.441
We believe they came back here after
they left you at the Birches' yesterday.

23:48.600 --> 23:51.171
They were looking for Anna's red whistle.

23:51.640 --> 23:53.165
<font color="#808080">LOKI:</font> Right.

23:53.720 --> 23:55.688
I read your statement.

23:56.520 --> 23:58.409
I'm Detective Loki.

23:58.920 --> 24:02.083
I'm heading up the investigation
into your daughter's disappearance.

24:02.240 --> 24:04.527
Please sit down.

24:06.560 --> 24:12.010
My son already told you that the guy was
inside the RV just watching them, right?

24:12.960 --> 24:15.884
We haven't found
any physical evidence inside the RV.

24:16.040 --> 24:18.566
Or his aunt's house where he lives.

24:18.960 --> 24:21.247
- Nothing?
<font color="#808080">LOKI:</font> - Alex Jones...

24:21.400 --> 24:24.370
...unfortunately has the I.Q.
of a 10-year-old.

24:24.600 --> 24:27.171
There's no way someone
with the I.Q. of a 10-year-old...

24:27.360 --> 24:29.886
...could abduct two girls
in broad daylight, and then...

24:30.160 --> 24:31.969
...somehow make them disappear.

24:33.040 --> 24:35.691
Well, how can he drive an RV?

24:36.560 --> 24:38.528
If he can't answer a question...

24:38.680 --> 24:41.365
Well, he has a legal Pennsylvania license.

24:41.520 --> 24:44.251
And he ran, right?
They said he tried to run away.

24:44.400 --> 24:48.246
Why"? Why? Why would he run?

24:48.400 --> 24:52.803
I've just spent 10 hours questioning this boy.
Okay? I hear what you're saying.

24:53.080 --> 24:54.570
Uh...

24:55.600 --> 24:59.491
Did you give him a lie detector?
You gave us a lie... Did you give him one?

24:59.680 --> 25:01.967
I understand what you're asking me.
Yes, we did.

25:02.120 --> 25:04.521
We gave him a lie detector,
and there's no way of...

25:04.680 --> 25:06.091
<font color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLES)</font>

25:06.960 --> 25:10.043
A lie detector doesn't work
if you don't understand the questions.

25:10.200 --> 25:13.488
Well, maybe he wasn't on his own.
How could he drive an RV...

25:13.640 --> 25:17.247
- ...if he has an I.Q. of a 10-year-old?<font color="#808080"> LOKI:</font>
- We're considering all possibilities.

25:17.400 --> 25:20.324
- I don't think you are considering...
<font color="#808080">LOKI:</font> - I hear what you're saying.

25:20.480 --> 25:23.131
Listen to me. Shut the fuck up
for a fucking second!

25:23.400 --> 25:25.050
<font color="#D900D9">(GRACE WHIMPERS)</font>

25:25.280 --> 25:28.602
This is what I'm gonna need you to do
for me. I need you to calm down.

25:30.280 --> 25:34.285
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.
Please listen to me for a second.

25:34.440 --> 25:37.046
<font color="#808080">LOKI:</font> Mr. Dover, I understand
this is an incredibly hard time.

25:37.200 --> 25:41.364
But I have every uniformed police officer
in this state looking for Anna.

25:41.560 --> 25:44.643
I don't understand what any of this means.
They said he ran.

25:44.800 --> 25:49.931
They said he tried to get away. I don't
understand why he would try to run away.

25:51.800 --> 25:54.565
We're considering all possibilities,
Mr. Dover.

25:54.720 --> 25:56.324
I hear what you're saying.

25:56.480 --> 26:00.280
I'm not crossing anybody off my list.
Just...

26:00.840 --> 26:02.842
...let me do my job.

26:07.320 --> 26:09.322
<font color="#D900D9">(CELL PHONE VIBRATES)</font>

26:16.000 --> 26:17.331
<font color="#808080">KELLER:</font> Hey!

26:17.840 --> 26:19.330
Detective!

26:20.280 --> 26:22.328
- Shit.
- Hey!

26:22.800 --> 26:25.963
He stays in custody
until my daughter's found, right?

26:26.120 --> 26:27.167
Right?

26:27.320 --> 26:30.210
We have a 48 hour hold on him
unless we bring charges.

26:30.400 --> 26:33.529
Well, charge him with something.
Charge him.

26:34.440 --> 26:37.967
- Mr. Dover, I understand what you're...
- Two girls have got to be worth...

26:38.120 --> 26:41.010
...whatever rule you break
to keep that asshole in custody.

26:41.200 --> 26:43.601
I know you can't promise me anything.
I understand.

26:43.760 --> 26:47.731
But I'm asking you to be sure.
Be 100 percent sure.

26:48.360 --> 26:49.885
Thank you.

26:51.200 --> 26:53.009
I appreciate it.

26:55.880 --> 26:58.565
So you're positive he's innocent,
but you want to hold him?

26:58.760 --> 27:00.524
<font color="#808080">LOKI:</font> Anna's father was
a mess this morning.

27:00.720 --> 27:04.202
- I understand. But it's not gonna happen.
- I was asking for one more day.

27:04.360 --> 27:06.647
Fuck you. Oh, no.

27:06.800 --> 27:10.486
Find his daughter, he'll forgive you.
You don't, he's gonna hate you anyway.

27:10.640 --> 27:12.290
So, what's next?

27:13.040 --> 27:16.601
<font color="#808080">LOKI:</font> - I'm knocking on doors all night.
- You're coming up on 24 hours missing...

27:16.760 --> 27:20.242
- ...and you have exactly shit.
- I've got nine level-three sex offenders...

27:20.400 --> 27:23.847
...living within a 10-mile radius
of Fairmont Circle. So if you don't mind.

27:24.000 --> 27:25.081
<font color="#808080">CAPTAIN:</font> - Then go.
- Yeah.

27:25.240 --> 27:26.526
Go.

27:28.240 --> 27:29.685
<font color="#D900D9">(DOOR CLOSES)</font>

27:37.400 --> 27:39.164
It's right here.

27:46.040 --> 27:49.249
<font color="#808080">MAN 1:</font> Look, I'm staying straight, okay?

27:49.400 --> 27:52.961
No, it's... Hey, look.
Look, I know you're...

27:54.000 --> 27:56.810
- I was...<font color="#808080"> LOKI:</font>
- Like yourself some German porn, huh?

27:56.960 --> 27:58.610
<font color="#808080">MAN 1:</font> Look, I was...

28:25.280 --> 28:27.760
<font color="#D900D9">(DOORBELL RINGING)</font>

28:34.640 --> 28:37.769
Father! Open up! It's the police!

28:37.920 --> 28:40.491
<font color="#D900D9">(DOORBELL RINGING)</font>

28:56.760 --> 28:58.649
<font color="#D900D9">(DOOR BANGS OPEN)</font>

28:58.840 --> 29:00.842
<font color="#D900D9">(MUSIC PLAYING ON TV)</font>

29:05.120 --> 29:09.045
<font color="#D900D9">(SNORING)</font>

29:15.120 --> 29:16.690
Father.

29:21.920 --> 29:23.490
Father.

29:28.800 --> 29:31.007
Mind if I take a look around?

29:53.360 --> 29:54.930
<font color="#D900D9">(SCOFFS)</font>

29:56.800 --> 29:58.723
Fucking drunk.

30:05.520 --> 30:07.045
<font color="#D900D9">(GRUNTS)</font>

30:08.280 --> 30:10.567
<font color="#D900D9">(GRUNTING)</font>

30:16.120 --> 30:17.884
What the fuck?

30:22.480 --> 30:24.084
Whoa.

30:31.080 --> 30:32.730
Fuck.

31:00.360 --> 31:02.442
Aah. Fuck.

32:05.480 --> 32:07.403
<font color="#D900D9">(SIGHS)</font>

32:11.600 --> 32:15.002
<font color="#808080">PRIEST:</font> Aah! Please, God, God!

32:15.200 --> 32:17.885
What's the name of your buddy down
there? What's the name?

32:18.080 --> 32:20.367
- I don't know his name.
- Huh? You don't know his name?

32:20.520 --> 32:22.329
- I don't know his name.
- You know what?

32:22.480 --> 32:26.883
I spent six years in Huntington Boys' Home.
You know the Huntington Boys' Home, right?

32:27.040 --> 32:30.362
Hurting a fuck like you'd be a treat.
Why don't you tell me his name?

32:30.520 --> 32:35.162
He didn't tell me his name.
He came to me for a confession.

32:35.320 --> 32:39.211
He said he'd killed 16 children.
He bragged about it.

32:39.360 --> 32:43.490
I convinced him to come back here.
He said he'd kill more.

32:43.640 --> 32:45.802
Sixteen children, huh?

32:45.960 --> 32:49.407
- All right, let's go, you fucking
chicken-hawk.<font color="#808080"> PRIEST:</font> - Aah!

33:10.040 --> 33:13.965
<font color="#D900D9">(DOGS BARKING)</font>

33:18.280 --> 33:20.442
<font color="#D900D9">(CELL PHONE RINGS)</font>

33:22.080 --> 33:24.401
- Hey.
<font color="#808080">GRACE:</font> <i>- They're letting him go.</i>

33:24.600 --> 33:26.204
- What?
<font color="#808080">GRACE:</font> <i>- The man.</i>

33:26.360 --> 33:28.442
<i>The police
said they're letting him go today.</i>

33:28.600 --> 33:31.888
Oh, okay. I'll take care of it.

33:33.200 --> 33:34.440
<font color="#808080">RALPH:</font> - Dad?
- Keep searching.

33:34.600 --> 33:36.762
Where are you going?

33:44.000 --> 33:46.606
<font color="#808080">AUNT:</font> They want you to
write your whole name.

33:52.960 --> 33:54.485
That's good.

33:59.520 --> 34:03.809
Mm-hm. Good job.
Now you give it to the man.

34:12.719 --> 34:17.248
All right. Come on. I don't want
you minding these people out here.

34:19.440 --> 34:21.966
Don't talk to them.
You've got nothing to say to them.

34:22.159 --> 34:24.049
<font color="#808080">REPORTER 1:</font> Hey!
<font color="#808080">REPORTER 2:</font> Alex!

34:24.199 --> 34:26.646
<font color="#808080">POLICEMAN:</font> Back, back.

34:27.080 --> 34:28.445
Let them walk.

34:28.600 --> 34:31.331
<font color="#D900D9">(REPORTERS CHATTERING INDISTINCTLY)</font>

34:31.480 --> 34:32.844
<font color="#D900D9">(TIRES SCREECHING)</font>

34:37.120 --> 34:38.849
<font color="#808080">REPORTER 3:</font> Alex!
<font color="#808080">REPORTER 4:</font> Come on, Alex.

34:39.000 --> 34:40.331
You took those kids, didn't you?

34:40.480 --> 34:43.130
I just want to talk.
He's a free man, I'm a free man!

34:43.840 --> 34:46.002
<font color="#808080">MAN 1:</font> No!
<font color="#808080">MAN 2:</font> Hey!

34:46.159 --> 34:48.766
Tell me what you did with them!
Tell me!

34:48.920 --> 34:50.603
They didn't cry until I left them.

34:50.760 --> 34:53.127
What did you say? What did you say?

34:53.280 --> 34:55.647
No, no! No!

34:55.800 --> 34:57.689
Fucking get off him!

34:57.840 --> 34:59.285
God. Get up!

34:59.440 --> 35:01.647
<font color="#808080">POLICEMAN 1:</font> Get him down! Get him down!

35:01.800 --> 35:03.802
<font color="#808080">POLICEMAN 2:</font> - Move back! Move back!
- Come on.

35:03.960 --> 35:08.682
Please, just let us go. Thanks for nothing.
We're fine. Thank you.

35:14.080 --> 35:18.608
Now, I know your dad was a guard
at Graterford.

35:18.800 --> 35:20.962
And I've got a daughter of my own, so...

35:21.120 --> 35:24.203
...we're gonna pretend this never happened.

35:24.920 --> 35:28.561
And as for Alex Jones, he has orders
not to leave the commonwealth.

35:28.720 --> 35:32.884
- What?
- Sir, I need you to go home. All right?

35:33.040 --> 35:35.691
- I need you to go home.
- What about what I just told you?

35:35.840 --> 35:37.410
Why aren't you sending someone
to arrest this guy?

35:37.560 --> 35:41.201
Tell Detective Loki what you just told me,
and he'll definitely look into it.

35:41.360 --> 35:42.725
Go ahead.

35:43.560 --> 35:48.168
That asshole you promised me you'd
keep in custody, right? And you didn't.

35:48.320 --> 35:51.244
When I grabbed him in the parking lot,
he said right to my face:

35:51.400 --> 35:54.722
"They didn't cry until I left them."
Right to my fucking face.

35:54.920 --> 35:56.763
He said that to you in the parking lot?

35:56.960 --> 35:59.645
Right now, yeah. What did I just say?
In the parking lot.

35:59.840 --> 36:02.081
Before you grabbed me off him.

36:03.400 --> 36:05.687
Did anyone else hear it besides you?

36:05.840 --> 36:10.164
I don't know. It was quiet. He said it to me.
He wanted me to know.

36:10.320 --> 36:12.163
<font color="#808080">LOKI:</font> Are you sure he said that?
- What?

36:12.760 --> 36:14.888
Are you sure that's what he said?

36:15.040 --> 36:18.681
Jesus Christ, you think I'm making this up?
Why would I make this up?

36:18.840 --> 36:20.285
- Hey, hey, hey.
- No. No.

36:20.440 --> 36:23.330
- Think about it. Why would I make this up?
- I'm not saying that.

36:23.480 --> 36:26.370
I'm just asking you a couple questions.
I will talk to him.

36:26.520 --> 36:30.411
- No, don't talk to him! Arrest him!
- Mr. Dover.

36:33.240 --> 36:35.288
What did I fucking tell you?

36:35.440 --> 36:38.091
What did I tell you? One more day.

36:39.680 --> 36:43.366
You sure you didn't say anything
to Mr. Dover in the parking lot today?

36:45.120 --> 36:48.044
Anything he could have
misinterpreted or...?

36:48.720 --> 36:50.131
I was right there.

36:50.280 --> 36:53.921
They didn't say anything to each other.
Man just attacked the boy.

36:55.040 --> 36:59.204
Nothing like "get away from me"
or "help" or...

36:59.400 --> 37:01.323
...anything like that?

37:02.480 --> 37:04.130
No.

37:07.200 --> 37:09.168
Can I speak to Alex alone for a minute?

37:13.640 --> 37:16.723
It's all right, sweetie.
I'll be right in the next room.

37:16.920 --> 37:18.888
<font color="#D900D9">(AUNT GROANS)</font>

37:29.320 --> 37:31.322
You love your aunt, don't you, Alex?

37:37.560 --> 37:38.641
Yes.

37:39.240 --> 37:43.370
If you know something you're not telling us,
she could go to jail for a very long time.

37:44.000 --> 37:46.048
Do you want that for her?

37:47.640 --> 37:49.688
After everything she's done for you?

37:50.800 --> 37:52.325
No.

38:07.720 --> 38:10.200
Mr. Dover, it's Detective Loki.

38:10.840 --> 38:13.730
- Have you arrested him?
<font color="#808080">LOKI:</font> <i>- Look, I just came from Alex Jones.</i>

38:13.880 --> 38:16.121
<i>He said he didn't say anything
to you in the lot.</i>

38:16.280 --> 38:20.171
I pushed him pretty hard, he didn't budge.
We can't waste any more time on this guy.

38:20.320 --> 38:24.166
You're gonna have to trust me.
I'll let you know if I have anything new...

38:24.360 --> 38:25.646
For the...

38:27.160 --> 38:29.003
Fucking A.

38:32.640 --> 38:35.484
<font color="#D900D9">(GRACE SOBBING)</font>

38:42.880 --> 38:46.248
<font color="#808080">GRACE:</font> The zipper on her coat was broken,
and I told her it didn't matter...

38:46.400 --> 38:48.926
...because we were just gonna go
right down the street.

38:49.080 --> 38:52.163
<font color="#808080">KELLER:</font> No. No.
<font color="#808080">GRACE:</font> Why hasn't she come home?

38:52.320 --> 38:54.607
It's been three days.

38:54.760 --> 38:58.287
Why can't you make her come home?

38:59.680 --> 39:01.682
I don't understand.

39:02.400 --> 39:06.564
I don't understand. It's been too long.

39:06.800 --> 39:09.770
Please make her come home.

