01:37:33.640 --> 01:37:36.007
<font color="#D900D9">(INDISTINCT CHATTERING)</font>

01:37:46.080 --> 01:37:47.764
<font color="#D900D9">(NANCY WHIMPERS)</font>

01:37:53.440 --> 01:37:56.284
<font color="#D900D9">(NANCY SOBBING SOFTLY)</font>

