01:42:42.000 --> 01:42:44.924
You're gonna bring her home?
She's dead. You can't do anything.

01:42:45.080 --> 01:42:48.243
You leave me and Mom here while you go out,
getting fucking drunk!

01:42:48.400 --> 01:42:51.768
- You think I can't smell on you?
- Shut up!

01:43:13.640 --> 01:43:15.802
<font color="#808080">CAPTAIN:</font> How long has this
Bob Taylor been working...

01:43:16.000 --> 01:43:17.729
...on this map?

01:43:18.200 --> 01:43:20.123
<font color="#808080">LOKI:</font> Three and a half hours.

01:43:20.440 --> 01:43:23.284
<font color="#808080">CAPTAIN:</font> Think this is gonna lead
to the bodies? I sure as shit don't.

01:43:23.440 --> 01:43:26.125
<font color="#808080">LOKI:</font> Do me a favor, captain.
Go fuck yourself.

01:43:26.280 --> 01:43:28.806
We weren't getting anywhere
questioning him.

01:43:33.480 --> 01:43:35.400
<font color="#808080">CAPTAIN:</font> That looks more
like a maze than a map.

01:43:35.560 --> 01:43:37.483
He's got a thing for mazes.

01:43:40.400 --> 01:43:44.200
I'm going home.
Call me if something happens.

01:43:50.280 --> 01:43:51.645
<font color="#D900D9">(LOKI SIGHS)</font>

01:43:56.360 --> 01:43:58.328
<font color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLING)</font>

01:44:09.000 --> 01:44:11.970
<font color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLING THEN HUMMING)</font>

01:44:19.560 --> 01:44:21.562
<font color="#D900D9">(BOB CONTINUES HUMMING)</font>

01:44:27.360 --> 01:44:30.364
Give me that card, John. The key card.

01:44:40.040 --> 01:44:42.008
All right, it's done now.

01:44:44.160 --> 01:44:46.049
Tell me what you're drawing.

01:44:47.520 --> 01:44:50.126
You said you're drawing a map.
That looks like a puzzle.

01:44:50.280 --> 01:44:52.089
You tell me what you're drawing.

01:44:54.440 --> 01:44:55.851
<font color="#D900D9">(HUMMING)</font>

